=== Testing internal access ===
=== Internal access (from within methods) ===

1. Using this.width:
Getting width: 100
Got: 100

2. Setting this.width = 150:
Setting width to: 150

3. Using bare width (no this.):
Getting width: 150
Got: 150

4. Setting bare width = 200:
Setting width to: 200

5. Reading height (read-only):
Getting height: 50
Got: 50

6. Writing depth (write-only):
Setting depth to: 30

7. Reading computed area:
Computing area: 10000
Got: 10000

=== External access (from main) ===

1. External read widget.width:
Getting width: 200
Got: 200

2. External write widget.width = 250:
Setting width to: 250

3. External read widget.height (read-only):
Getting height: 50
Got: 50

4. External write widget.depth (write-only):
Setting depth to: 35

5. External read widget.area (computed):
Computing area: 12500
Got: 12500
